<li>Microsoft Word 2003 Viewer</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Microsoft Project 2000 Service Release 1 - <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?familyid=019b11fc-00b8-451c-ab3c-772780d4c46a" data-linktype="external">Download the update (KB920906)</a></li>
<li>Microsoft Office 2000 Multilanguage Packs — <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?familyid=b5a087f8-74d2-4184-9986-23ab3c4ef7f2" data-linktype="external">Download the update (KB920906)</a></li>
<li>Microsoft Project 2002 Service Pack 1 - <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?familyid=d162c366-c5e7-4850-b773-1fe669faeeaf" data-linktype="external">Download the update (KB920816)</a></li>
<li>Microsoft Visio 2002 Service Pack 2 - <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?familyid=b4d2e182-0997-46bc-94ac-b4b0a523c51c" data-linktype="external">Download the update (KB920816)</a></li>
<li>Microsoft Learning Essentials 1.0, 1.1, and 1.5 for Microsoft Office - <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?familyid=6215bd5b-1cb3-4fed-b08c-c31a88a75ebd" data-linktype="external">Download the update (KB929437)</a></li>
